{"tid":1536912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醒未啊香港人？","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:31:18.000Z","uid":161483,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e94e1139b2cea8a8dfb4c27950388057ee7f3b47","tid":1536912,"uid":161483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:57:54.000Z","msg":"醒啦屌你老母<br />\n依家有人比狗打到頸椎受傷<br />\n有人懷疑被狗謀殺<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 點解你地仲可以咁嬉皮笑臉 </span>"},{"pid":"301ac237c2bb186f48fb10d0a88ea39cceaaef43","tid":1536912,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da66daca4dbef26e994370854a2e416c9cbcb776","tid":1536912,"uid":161483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"乜撚野睇佢聽日點回應？<br />\n點回應關你撚事？<br />\n預咗佢搵藉口兜啦<br />\n咁又點？<br />\n你又網上屌返佢？<br />\n有用咩？"},{"pid":"a38a112141b7d293b2625cf67ace458e6f603348","tid":1536912,"uid":161483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"醒啦好唔好<br />\n班狗已經失去理智<br />\n你譴責有撚用咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 譴責救港？ </span>"},{"pid":"8e033562c9160e096a52da0f4c136e34654876ae","tid":1536912,"uid":161483,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:01:54.000Z","msg":"一班人圍觀人點？<br />\n無人幫手<br />\n說好的齊上齊落？<br />\n打狗救人？<br />\n你老味口口聲聲話手足<br />\n你當人係乜啊？"},{"pid":"b5c9388688fa8881d8350f618da394d0fe405711","tid":1536912,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"［超長文］前線革命宣言：830隻狗係我地斬嘅<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agmuFrU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agmuFrU</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打們唔洗絕望<br />\n依個方向就正確"},{"pid":"174c7fa3189518b1988c4851b133d41f38b9f855","tid":1536912,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0cf6b143c0a1522b176a5e2a8746abd08046e0","tid":1536912,"uid":161483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:03:08.000Z","msg":"幅meme講得啱<br />\n不核彈都唔割好偉大？<br />\n人地為你付出一生<